For planets:
1)
PlanetSim 2 5e10 0.1 2 'planetsIn.txt' 5000 >> EV

grep EV Earth >> Eout, Venus >> Vout

for lots of planets (ie particles)

2)
PlanetSim 2 5e10 1 11 'particlesIn.txt' 5000 >> partsout

grep files to p1, p2, etc... then load 'AnimateParts.gnu'


3)
PlanetSim 3 5e10 1 1 'in3d.txt' 1500 >> 3dOut

grep into E3out, use the 3d .gnu file to animate a splot.
